{"tid":92493,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點先可以成功戒賭? (1)","createTime":"2017-01-23T15:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T15:38:55.000Z","uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68393131efa1d92be4cf197410173baab50a9b4a","tid":92493,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:21:43.000Z","msg":"好鍾意足球呢種運動<br />\n基本上日日都會接觸<br />\n睇波踢波睇足球新聞<br />\n一睇波就會忍唔住想賭 覺得買左再睇先會刺激D<br />\n自問定力同自制力真係唔夠<br />\n有冇手足有成功戒賭經歷可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(波馬賭場股票都ok)"},{"pid":"054a0fd923562792eb896a13f1be099df8dc5846","tid":92493,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:22:18.000Z","msg":"Del了app"},{"pid":"dc77b1b5941ebda151d3e29fd8f786ecca6fc162","tid":92493,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:23:35.000Z","msg":"試下 落馬會買真飛 唔好多app不停賭"},{"pid":"9ebd8e1b8e9af64238cb0a6d59f7a8ad51040208","tid":92493,"uid":12973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:27:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下 落馬會買真飛 唔好多app不停賭</blockquote><br />\n同路"},{"pid":"e1017633c5626e80a1952a6db16563bb015497ed","tid":92493,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:27:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Del了app</blockquote><br />\n個app有時check比分同幾點開波都好方便<br />\n同埋六合彩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9a6ee8eb21d84aae9869b4c389aacbf3f2c40c","tid":92493,"uid":4461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:27:20.000Z","msg":"你有無贏錢？ 輸到仆街你自然唔會賭 想針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我就是一個例子</span>"},{"pid":"0ecd26c8c59eb918f2c2ca092fcc2c564cefd742","tid":92493,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試下 落馬會買真飛 唔好多app不停賭</blockquote><br />\n同路</blockquote><br />\n完全戒甩有冇人試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9587311b8e8e83a280b43face48614b41ef848","tid":92493,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:29:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有無贏錢？ 輸到仆街你自然唔會賭 想針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我就是一個例子</span></blockquote><br />\n未到仆街既...始終都係睇果一場先會買<br />\n但輸多過贏囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你知啦,狗會D賠率咁西,輸一場=贏兩場<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc3d90832e83a35836107096e3b3e39bf9495bb","tid":92493,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:29:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試下 落馬會買真飛 唔好多app不停賭</blockquote><br />\n同路</blockquote><br />\n完全戒甩有冇人試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為你個每日睇好一場買完就算 變咗唔會好沈迷 又唔會輸好多 其實有得贏 同你麻煩唔買"},{"pid":"c9370e4050f5046c706127cfe9b1adf4086a21cf","tid":92493,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試下 落馬會買真飛 唔好多app不停賭</blockquote><br />\n同路</blockquote><br />\n完全戒甩有冇人試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為你個每日睇好一場買完就算 變咗唔會好沈迷 又唔會輸好多 其實有得贏 同你麻煩唔買</blockquote><br />\n明白既...但都係治標唔治本,輸錢會影響心情又會想大注追數<br />\n長遠都係戒甩佢最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c02193148d9cd902d73ce1004988934df2e5910","tid":92493,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Del了app</blockquote><br />\n個app有時check比分同幾點開波都好方便<br />\n同埋六合彩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗咩用app先check到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8828caff289c928770ee801ce383ee88000b3f","tid":92493,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:38:55.000Z","msg":"輸少少咪當娛樂囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}